column5:
Hi,

My client owns elioverbey.com. While seeking out potential buyers for this domain name your company came up as a potential suitor for it.

I am reaching out to a number of companies who might have an interest in buying elioverbey.com and I would appreciate if you would let me know if you would like to discuss it further.

My client uses Sedo.com to transact, and I am happy to guide you through the transfer process to ensure the domain name is in your possession.

Regards,

John Baker
Domain Name Broker
